<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub45.ezboard.com/utulweyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tulweyen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guild Master</span><br> <font color=#660000>(2/21/01 9:24:51 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Essence of Moonlight</span><hr size=1> If any Illuvitae members would like to get this armor, I have an Essence of Moonlight I can give you.<br>
