- Tul <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub45.ezboard.com/beverquest6820.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=xaeria>Xaeria</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#660000>(2/21/01 3:17:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Components</span><hr size=1> On the negative side, enchanting the armor requires a level 49 enchanter and a blue diamond as a compontent.  Maybe Verant should look at the cost vs. reward for this...<br>
