Xaeria <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub45.ezboard.com/uceescritdabossalini.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ceescrit da Bossalini</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Commander in Chief</span><br> <font color=#660000>(2/21/01 3:35:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Components</span><hr size=1> A blue diamond?  You have to be @#$% me!<br>
